<eesti>"&sect; 84. </eesti>
<inglise>"&sect; 84. </inglise>
<eesti>Tee ja raudtee, liiklusvahendi ning side-, signalisatsiooni- ja energiaseadme rikkumine </eesti>
<inglise>Damaging of road, railway, vehicle and communications equipment, signalling installations and energy equipment </inglise>
<eesti>Tee v&otilde;i raudtee, liiklusvahendi v&otilde;i side-, signalisatsiooni- v&otilde;i energiaseadme tahtliku purustamise v&otilde;i rikkumise eest, mis p&otilde;hjustas v&otilde;i v&otilde;is p&otilde;hjustada rongi- v&otilde;i lennu&otilde;nnetuse, laevaavarii, liiklus&otilde;nnetuse, transpordi v&otilde;i side normaalse t&ouml;&ouml; rikkumise, h&auml;ire energia tootmise v&otilde;i jaotamise s&uuml;steemis, - karistatakse vabadusekaotusega kolmest kuni kaheteistk&uuml;mne aastani." </eesti>
<inglise>Deliberate destruction or damaging of a road, railway or vehicle or of communications equipment, signalling installations or energy equipment which caused or could have caused a rail or aircraft accident, a marine casualty, a traffic accident, an obstruction to the normal operation of transport or communications, or a failure in the energy production or distribution system, is punishable by three to twelve years' imprisonment." </inglise>
